These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
City: hannover, miami, colone, marseilles
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| City    | miami  | marseilles | colone    | hannover       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| Game   | scrabble   | monopoly | poker | mah-jongg        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
House: colonial, art-deco, futuristic, tower
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, disco, techno, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the tower house is on the right of the fan of techno##1
3. the musician is on the right of the futuristic house##1
4. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of punk is the fisherman##1
6. the fan of trance is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| House        | futuristic   | art-deco | colonial     | tower      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | trance   | techno     | punk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, snooker, whist
There 4 different types of food: mango, banana, corn, radish
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person eating radish is on the far left##1
4. the person playing whist is the person eating corn##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person eating banana##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the person playing backgammon is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | backgammon | scrabble | snooker | whist |
| Food   | radish       | banana    | mango | corn     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
There 4 different types of food: corn, lemon, cherry, mango
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, amber, green, coral
1. the freelancer is the person who likes coral##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1
6. the person eating corn is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Food       | lemon     | mango      | corn     | cherry      |
| Color   | amber | lilac         | coral      | green        |

