.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, lawyer, designer, photographer
House: tower, cottage, futuristic, cape-cod
1. the lawyer is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the cottage house is on the right of the security-guard##1
4. the tower house is the designer##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the cottage house##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the lawyer##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Job   | designer  | security-guard        | photographer  | lawyer       |
| House         | tower | futuristic    | cottage | cape-cod |

