.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, skiing, badminton, parkour
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, september, may
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Sport           | skiing | badminton | parkour | skateboarding |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Birthday   | may   | august     | september | february       |

