.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, ship, boat, trike
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, skydiving, video-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, dahlia, aconite, iris
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is the person driving the boat##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Transport          | snowmobile  | trike | boat   | ship     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking   | baking  | skydiving |
| Flower   | aconite         | poppy  | dahlia | iris  |

