.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, iris, bellflower, begonia
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, dancing, camping, filmmaking
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, french, nigerian, pakistani
1. the person who growsiris is the nigerian##1
2. the pakistani is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the pakistani is the person who growsbellflower##1
7. the french is on the left of the pakistani##1
8. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Flower      | begonia | bellflower     | dahlia | iris |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | reading | camping       | dancing    |
| Nationality   | french   | pakistani | canadian    | nigerian |

