.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
4 different games are played: billiard, go, mah-jongg, poker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, jazz, punk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, march, august
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person playing go##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Game          | mah-jongg        | poker   | go  | billiard   |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | punk     | d&b    | jazz       |
| Birthday         | december | september | march | august |

