.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, puzzles, camping, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, doctor, pilot, nurse
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the doctor##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the pilot is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | camping | writing | hiking        |
| Job       | nurse | teacher  | doctor | pilot     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

