1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the videographer##1
7. the owner of the hamster is the person traveling to hamburg##1
8. the owner of the ferret is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | bartender  | videographer | photographer  | social-worker |
| Pet       | ferret | hedgehog        | lizard | hamster       |
| City   | marseilles   | rome          | berlin          | hamburg       |

