.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, cooking, dancing, traveling
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, january, april
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, white, grey, lavender
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who likes grey##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling   | dancing   | card-games | cooking |
| Birthday   | january | june | february   | april |
| Color   | lavender     | fuchsia  | grey  | white  |

