.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, pakistani, canadian, russian
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lavender, black, orange
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, skateboarding, skiing
1. the pakistani is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who likes orange##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Nationality         | russian | pakistani    | argentine        | canadian |
| Color   | lavender     | black     | orange        | fuchsia   |
| Sport         | sailing   | lacrosse | skateboarding | skiing  |

