.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo, cricket, handball
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, pakistani, russian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, daffodil, balloon-flower, amaryllis
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the russian##1
3. the canadian is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
8. the indonesian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | water-polo   | handball  | skateboarding    | cricket    |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | canadian  | indonesian |
| Flower     | amaryllis  | daffodil | balloon-flower | daisy        |

