.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, tea, water
4 different games are played: go, canasta, billiard, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, engineer, electrician, videographer
1. the freelancer is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the engineer is on the right of the videographer##1
5. the person playing chess is the person drinking water##1
6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the electrician##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the person playing go##1
8. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee        | water    | iced-tea | tea      |
| Game   | go        | chess   | canasta  | billiard  |
| Job         | videographer | engineer | electrician   | freelancer |

