.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, turkish, spanish, colombian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, hip-hop, folk, classical
1. the colombian is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the turkish is the fan of folk##1
5. the colombian is on the left of the spanish##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the spanish##1
7. the spanish is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality          | canadian     | colombian   | spanish | turkish |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | superhero | fantasy   |
| Music-Genre           | classical    | hip-hop     | rock      | folk     |

