.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, funk, punk
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, pineapple, apple, spinach
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person eating apple##1
2. the person drinking fanta is the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the fan of funk is the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
7. the person eating apple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage           | iced-tea  | water | fanta  | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | d&b       | electronic | punk      |
| Food   | pineapple | watermelon  | spinach    | apple    |

