.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-18::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, bellflower, iris, azalea
House: modern, gothic-revival, tower, colonial
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who growslily##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the modern house##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
6. the modern house is on the left of the colonial house##1
7. the person who growsiris is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | lily | bellflower | iris | azalea |
| House         | gothic-revival | modern | colonial  | tower  |
| Transport     | roller  | snowmobile | van     | subway  |

