.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, october, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, handball, water-polo, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, taxi, trike
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Birthday       | july | november | december | october |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | handball  | badminton   | water-polo      |
| Transport   | car        | taxi  | trike   | bus         |

