.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, engineer, scientist, security-guard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, november, june, september
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall, swisher, old-henry
1. the engineer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is the swisher-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
7. the security-guard is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | scientist  | dressmaker | security-guard |
| Birthday   | september   | january | november   | june      |
| Cigar         | blend | swisher    | pall-mall   | old-henry         |

 